des:
The Encircle LGBTQ Family & Youth Resource Center works with youth and families to improve relationships and to reduce the risk of suicide, drug abuse, and homelessness for LGBTQ youth. 

We invite you to visit our resource center, follow our Facebook page, or learn more about us on the web at encircletogether.org
